text.tspan: Per capita CO₂ emissions in 2017 vs 1990
Per capita emissions of carbon dioxide (CO₂) in the year 2017 versus 1990 emissions. Countries which lie above
the grey line had higher per capita emissions in 2017 than in 1990; countries below the line had lower per capita
Source: Our World in Data based on Global Carbon Project and UN Population
